-- Harmony Says Joel Gold Production for the September Quarter May be Halved
-- Alastair Reed
-- 2010-07-08T12:57:57Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-08/harmony-says-joel-gold-production-for-the-september-quarter-may-be-halved.html

          
          
             Harmony Gold Mining Ltd. said gold
production at its Joel operation in South Africa during the
September quarter will “possibly be halved” as a result of a
decision to carry out repairs at a shaft.  
          
          


  


        